Feature: AT-1 Policy and Procedures
  As a system administrator
  I want to develop, document, and disseminate policies and procedures
  So that awareness and training are implemented effectively

  Scenario: Develop awareness and training policy
    Given organization-defined personnel or roles
    When developing the awareness and training policy
    Then the policy should address purpose, scope, roles, responsibilities, management commitment, coordination among organizational entities, and compliance
    And the policy should be consistent with applicable laws, executive orders, directives, regulations, policies, standards, and guidelines

  Scenario: Develop procedures for awareness and training
    Given organization-defined personnel or roles
    When developing procedures for the awareness and training
    Then the procedures should facilitate the implementation of the awareness and training policy and associated controls

  Scenario: Designate an official to manage policy and procedures
    Given organization-defined official
    When designating the official
    Then the official should be responsible for managing the development, documentation, and dissemination of the awareness and training policy and procedures

  Scenario: Review and update awareness and training policy
    Given organization-defined frequency and events
    When reviewing and updating the awareness and training policy
    Then the policy should be reviewed following the organization-defined frequency and events

  Scenario: Review and update awareness and training procedures
    Given organization-defined frequency and events
    When reviewing and updating the awareness and training procedures
    Then the procedures should be reviewed following the organization-defined frequency and events
